Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:07.63,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Nishimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:09.32,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Nishimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:12.77,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,You're at the head of the class again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:15.78,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,I was worried with your grades dropping there for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.95,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,but it looks like you've straightened out your act.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.23,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because entrance exams are looming...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:26.19,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Or maybe it's thanks to the disappearance of the only thing that got in your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:45.33,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Pass it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:55.24,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,I never thought they'd agree to let us up here, but I'm glad they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:59.46,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,I heard some third-year thug was monopolizing the key up 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:03.40,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Hi! Richie-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:05.82,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I'm playing volleyball with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:07.25,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Wanna join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:11.63,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Nah. I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:15.55,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,Richie-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:20.14,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,I know you're lonely without Kawabuchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:21.97,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,but you should just get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:25.05,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:25.99,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:26.33,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Mukae!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:28.28,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Are you looking for Nishimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:30.45,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:35.71,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,It's so cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:39.76,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,I love milkshakes when it starts getting cold outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:45.84,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Hey, earth to Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:46.77,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:51.45,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're worried about Kawabuchi's disappearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:54.35,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, there's that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:56.02,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:57.49,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,It's Nishimi, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:01.32,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Like, you haven't been able to talk to him at all or walk home together lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.28,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Ritsu, you can't wait forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.43,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,You need to make things happen yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:10.21,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:11.79,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Isn't that Nishimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:19.32,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.94,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Were you eating ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.70,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You've got whipped cream on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.23,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um, Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.42,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Are you coming back to the basement today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.10,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.20,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:37.98,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,With entrance exams coming up, I've decided not to go for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.25,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.56,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:43.40,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Tell Pops that I'm sorry for not being able to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:44.74,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well, see ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:45.74,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.18,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:50.00,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Why not study at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.05,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,The shop's closed today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.03,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:01.51,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,He's off stocking up, so it's just me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:06.43,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.19,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I'll clean up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:18.42,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,That's my favorite one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.13,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I always have it out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.89,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Both of you look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.89,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Look at Sentaro's face—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.55,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Stop talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:31.69,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Should we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:34.00,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,English and math, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:43.20,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,So first of all, the word order is reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:47.80,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,This "so" comes before, and the subject and verb change places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:52.27,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.35,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um... I'm sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:05:01.58,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking about your feelings when I showed you that picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:07.78,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Sentaro leaving hit you the hardest, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.54,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:14.18,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Even if he's not around, I've still got you, Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.90,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:42.73,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Don't! Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.39,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, w-wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.74,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm glad he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:53.90,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Now I can be alone with you whenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.25,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.16,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.38,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,How could you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.98,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You're happy that Sentaro is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:11.05,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Even if you're joking, I don't want to hear such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.36,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:44.26,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu, I haven't been able to say this before,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.64,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but I'm going to a college in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.10,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'll go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.03,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.13,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}The lowest of the low!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:11.49,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.53,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did things turn out like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:18.79,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5\fs37\an6\c&H404042&\fnAver\b1\t(1614,2023,\blur0.7)\pos(1068,348)}East \NHigh \NGrad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:32.44,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,They didn't call Kawabuchi's name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.03,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:37.06,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Everyone's going their separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:40.65,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,We'll all forget being here in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.56,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,Nishimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:49.57,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,I won't ever forget the performance you two did at the festival last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.45,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:59.37,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Maruo? Could I have the second button on your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.59,Default,Maruo,0,0,0,,Sure, if that'd make you happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:05.00,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:09.51,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure if I'd be able to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:11.21,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was crying my eyes out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.01,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:21.62,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Farewell and good riddance to this damned slope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:24.84,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Don't go trudging up the thing tomorrow out of habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:51.80,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:55.40,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,So you're going off to a college in Tokyo too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:57.55,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Well, it'll probably get a little lonely around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:01.39,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Nah, we can't get gloomy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.88,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It's great news, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:04.51,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:06.81,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Ritsuko was accepted at the college nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.57,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Hey, Ritsuko! Come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:14.35,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Richie-rich got into college! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.07,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.33,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You can stay there, but please listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.16,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:31.59,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You may not want to listen to me, but just hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:37.22,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,The reason I came here was to see your smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:42.85,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Your smile always encouraged me, even when things were rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:48.38,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I never knew that feeling before meeting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.24,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,So thank you, Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.61,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Meeting you was a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.51,Default,Aunt,0,0,0,,Call us as soon as you arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:13.44,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:16.13,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,Kaoru, write me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:18.27,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.95,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:23.46,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}The sleeper express train, Sakura, will depart for Tokyo on track one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:25.72,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Its next stop will be Haiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.31,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}All passengers, please get on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:27.31,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.04,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.69,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Here, a little going-away present.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.15,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thanks, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:36.88,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.65,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Is Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:40.51,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.66,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,But there's a lunch in there that she made for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.70,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Well, take care, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.21,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I will. You too, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:54.01,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.23,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Ritsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.03,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:04.91,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,When you're sick, you're apt to lose heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.10,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,but like they say, sickness and health start with the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:10.29,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Doctor, you have a good head on your shoulders for someone so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:11.95,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:14.02,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm still a rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:16.29,Default,Nurse,0,0,0,,Dr. Nishimi, we've got an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.78,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.37,0:12:42.82,Default,Co-worker,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:45.86,Default,Co-worker,0,0,0,,there's a free bed in the nap room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.95,Default,Co-worker,0,0,0,,Why don't you get a little rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.49,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No, if I rest now, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.87,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I won't be able to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:59.43,Default,Co-worker,0,0,0,,Yeah, being a resident on the night shift is even harder than they said it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:01.68,Default,Co-worker,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:02.96,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Tell me about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:09.47,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our guest today is a pop star, a singer, and an actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.34,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please welcome Matsuoka Seiji to the studio!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.98,0:13:16.23,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs70\fnBPreplay\b1\c&HFCFBF9&\blur0.6\pos(633,531)}Guest: Matsuoka Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:16.23,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5\blur0.6\fs70\fnBPreplay\b1\c&H373839&\3c&H2A2B2C&\pos(633,531)}Guest: Matsuoka Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:16.23,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello! I'm Matsuoka Seiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.34,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Let's start right off with a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.34,0:13:21.29,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}What do you like more, singing or acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:20.62,Default,Co-worker,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.24,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:25.24,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}I like them both...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.61,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,That's a classmate from high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.30,Default,Co-worker,0,0,0,,Huh? My little sister goes nuts over that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:29.74,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}And I like jazz, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.13,Default,Co-worker,0,0,0,,Hey! Get me an autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.58,Default,Host,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Oh, jazz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:41.11,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. So Matsuoka's dream came true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:43.78,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:53.87,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:57.81,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Kaoru?! Kaoru, is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:00.42,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:04.57,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,How wonderful! You've become a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.83,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:12.16,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm six months along. Junichi wants a girl, but I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:15.31,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I think he'd spoil her rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.35,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.54,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Have you been good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.92,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Do you still play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:21.96,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:26.72,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'd heard that Sentaro took off, but you've never seen him since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.47,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:35.00,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,This is no time to be catching up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:38.39,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,There's something I've been carrying around to show everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:42.06,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,A friend from back home sent me this picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:45.38,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,but don't you think the person on the far left looks like someone we know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.57,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:55.25,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Can I borrow this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:06.15,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:11.09,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been trying to forget him all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.36,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}but my heart is beating so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:19.10,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I can stop this rhythm in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:23.11,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,If you want the church, it's at the top of the slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:26.23,Default,Sailor,0,0,0,,Young priest? Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:30.61,Default,Man,0,0,0,,The priest here has been around for years and years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:35.92,Default,Farmer,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think he helps raise the orphans from around the prefecture...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:37.62,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,He raises children?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:41.47,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Yes, you mean the priest-in-training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:45.54,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Though I hear he does nothing but cause trouble for the poor priest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.38,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.88,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:56.39,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:24.92,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't see this every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.16,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.48,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Pick me up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.75,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:59.53,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I always thought this day might come eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.91,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Looks like it's today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:40.11,Default,Priest,0,0,0,,Enough! What do you two think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:45.12,Default,Priest,0,0,0,,I told you that you can only play on special occasions, but yet again, you just do as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.49,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.61,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Run, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:49.77,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:49.58,OP,,0,0,0,,{OP}{First frame of OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.21,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}What should I do{\fncinnamon cake}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:59.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}I forgot who I was before I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.18,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}The wind brushes my cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Lullaby of Birdland
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:10.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Kicking the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:14.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}a frail shadow stretches on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:19.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}It's like a neverending summer break
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:24.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}It feels like sneaking into a pool
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:30.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Hey, let's just swim with our clothes on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Hop{\fncinnamon cake}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:34.04,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}A spiral of sensational temptation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:38.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Those beats that sting me are strange
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:41.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}They burn out and disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:41.76,Default,,20,20,20,,{\an1\fs35\bord1.4\q2}It's been so long! How are you? I'm writing now because there's something I want to tell you, \NRitsuko. A friend of mine from back home got married at a church, and in a photo of the ceremony\N that she sent me, there's a priest who looks just like Sentaro. I'm not sure of it, but thought it\N would be worth looking into. The church is on a small island, so it should be easy to find. I just\N wrote this postcard to let you know. If you find anything out, please write back. \NYours truly, Yurika Fukahori {separate as needed}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.05,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}I'm fine with those crazy days
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:44.76,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Swinging with such electric speed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Surround
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.43,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}What's that dance called{\fncinnamon cake}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}It won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:21:01.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Don't go, it lingers on  in my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Melody is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.70,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}like a love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:21.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{ED}{First frame after To Be Continued}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:28.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I waited for you on that road downhill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:42.01,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}Our promise to meet after school always held a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:51.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I was weak and distorted, and seemed to easily crack under pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:22:03.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}You were the one who gave me wings then
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:12.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I wish I could say I love you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:23.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}while you're looking for a faint light in the sky at dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:35.56,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}The letter I wrote in the corner of my textbook
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.56,0:22:43.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}will never reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:49.07,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}and nothing will ever change {BEST FUCKING SHOW}
